The original ainovel-cli is the upstream engine. OUMStudio-Novel adds a
Vietnamese prose-quality layer (hard gates for em dash / English leakage,
30+ continuity rules, 9 Vietnamese styles, the Nacharium critique council,
premium dark/bright EPUB export) and bundles a suite of process skills
(cw-* family, novel-guardian, novel-master, novelcore-ai, forge-novel-guard)
on top of that engine.

